  "text": "We used genomic data of CEU, CHB and YRI populations in 1KGP. Tajima's D value, iHS and p were calculated for 3kb intervals. XP-CLR were calculated for 2kb intervals. All these measurements were acquired through the 1000 Genomes Selection Browser [CITATION_1] .",
